author: vmassol
msg: Removed the maven.clover.jar property that was used to override the default Clover jar. This property was not working (it requires Ant 1.6) and is no needed anymore as Cenqua has cleanly separated the Clover jar from the Clover license. You only need to point maven.clover.license.path to your license file.
